{"tid":576508,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"商台：波叔相信出現市民爭相報考DSE的機會較少。","createTime":"2018-03-01T03:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T10:57:23.000Z","uid":57448,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e943e8f60adede7d2d55e89fdc72f82710cf3015","tid":576508,"uid":57448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:15:06.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波昨日公佈的財政預算案提出為明年參加文憑試（DSE）的考生代繳考試費，成為網民最熱烈討論的預算案措施之一，更有不少人表示將會報考，更分享報考攻略。陳茂波今早出席電台節目時，被問到會否沒有預料到可能有大量市民報考，變相增加原來DSE考生的壓力。商台新聞引述陳茂波回應稱，措施目的是希望關顧年輕人，除了支援學校考生，亦支援自修生，希望減輕他們的壓力，如果有人因為免考試費而多讀書並無問題。他相信出現有關情況的機會較少。<br />\n<br />\n一齊搞串個party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c0ac351154ab7738657cf78c7a68f7f68a499e","tid":576508,"uid":57448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"佢盈餘都估少千二億<br />\n真係唔知今年會有幾多人報DSE喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf1c322186931fd354ac7e872da4a04165616c4","tid":576508,"uid":89433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea22e96079e5d154b7aa1b8e84c63264c441d51","tid":576508,"uid":57448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"重點：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦支援自修生</span>"},{"pid":"423497722f5ec349ef0a59b692316fdc39852d32","tid":576508,"uid":653,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:40:50.000Z","msg":"如果有人因為免考試費而多讀書並無問題<br />\n戇鳩我去攬炒一定會讀書既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bd1165684884c0b36e8ce55cb7ecbcee3c59dd","tid":576508,"uid":57448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"423497722f5ec349ef0a59b692316fdc39852d32","tid":576508,"uid":653,"like":4,"dislike